Second Department,

April, 1938.

(April 1, 1938.) William Hughes, Respondent, v. John H. Ryder, Appellant.

Motion to dismiss appeal dismissed in view of the decision on the appeal (post, p. 677), decided herewith. Motion to open default granted. Present — Lazansky, P. J., Hagarty, Carswell, Adel and Close, JJ.
